claim.claim-text:
1. A method of treating a bone condition in a subject by a health care provider comprising
(a) obtaining image data from said subject, which image data includes image data of one or more bones of said subject;
(b) analyzing, in a computer system, the image data obtained in step (a) to derive quantitative information on bone structure, wherein the analyzed image data includes image data of trabecular bone;
(c) diagnosing a bone condition based on the analysis of step (b); and
(d) selecting a suitable treatment to said subject based on said diagnosis.

8. A method of treating a bone disease in a patient, the method comprising the steps of:
(a) obtaining image data from said patient, wherein said image data includes image data of one or more trabecular bones;
(b) assessing bone mineral density in at least one anatomic region with said image data;
(c) assessing bone structure in said region to obtain quantitative information on bone structure;
(d) combining said assessments of bone mineral density and bone structure to evaluate bone disease;
(e) selecting an initial therapy based on the evaluation of bone disease; and
(f) administering said initial therapy to said patient.

13. A method of treating a bone condition in a subject comprising:
(a) deriving quantitative information, in a computer system, on bone structure from image data of said subject obtained at an initial time point;
(b) comparing the derived information on bone structure to a database of bone structure measurements obtained from selected subjects;
(c) diagnosing a bone condition based on the comparison of step (b);
(d) selecting and administering a suitable initial treatment to said subject based on said diagnosis;
(e) deriving quantitative information, in a computer system, on bone structure from image data of said subject obtained at a later time point;
(f) comparing said quantitative information obtained in step (e) to said quantitative information obtained in step (a); and
(g) selecting and administering a later treatment to said subject based on said comparison in step (f).
